wmsLayer.title: GA0305 St George 1m
wmsLayer.description: This layer is a bathymetry grid of the survey area near Cape St George Lighthouse from marine surveys GA0303, GA0305, GA0309 and GA0312, collected around Jervis Bay, New South Wales. The data is gridded at one metre resolution. A total of eleven areas were surveyed at various resolutions. The colour ramp for the WMS is stretched between 2-60 metres water depth. The dataset can be downloaded at the following URL http://services.ga.gov.au/metadata-gateway/metadata/record/72004.
